data.description: Stunning corner home in the Village of Escaya, perfect for entertaining and/or raising a family. This 5bed/4bath corner lot home features an open floorpan, newer countertops, update light fixtures, fully paid solar and modern design throughout the home. Spacious 3 car garage perfect for storage, home gyms, etc. Amazing mountain/canyon views from the master bedroom and backyard. Home has been taken care of very well and is move in ready! This lovely neighborhood  features walking trails, a brand new park, dog park and Clubhouse with Pool and Gym.
